                "invention-title": [
                    "Method and system for preparing hydrogen-containing product by coupling coal gasification with high-temperature electrolyzed water",
                    "一种煤气化耦合高温电解水制备含氢产品的方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of coal gasification processes, in particular to a method and a system for preparing a hydrogen-containing product by coupling coal gasification with high-temperature electrolyzed water. The method comprises the following steps: A) gasifying dry pulverized coal/coal water slurry to obtain synthesis gas; the required oxygen is prepared from high-temperature electrolyzed water; b) performing acid gas fine removal on the synthesis gas through a medium-temperature pressure swing adsorption process; and C) mixing the finely removed synthesis gas with hydrogen obtained by high-temperature water electrolysis, adjusting the ratio of hydrogen to hydrogen, and carrying out a synthesis reaction to obtain a hydrogen-containing product. The water-gas shift section is replaced by a high-temperature electrolyzed water system, the carbon-hydrogen ratio is adjusted by providing hydrogen, and meanwhile, the water-gas shift section is prevented from discharging a large amount of CO2. In addition, the high-temperature electrolyzed water provides oxygen for coal gasification; after hydrogen components are adjusted, redundant impurity gas after coal gasification is efficiently and flexibly removed through a specific adsorption process, so that the problems that the utilization rate of carbon atoms of traditional chemicals prepared through coal gasification is not high, and a large amount of CO2 is discharged due to the fact that the carbon-hydrogen ratio is adjusted through water-gas shift are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及煤气化工艺技术领域，尤其涉及一种煤气化耦合高温电解水制备含氢产品的方法及系统。所述方法包括：A)将干煤粉/水煤浆进行气化，得到合成气；所需氧气由高温电解水制得；B)通过中温变压吸附工艺对合成气进行酸性气体精脱；C)将精脱后的合成气与高温电解水得到的氢气混合，调整碳氢比，进行合成反应，得到含氢产品。水气变换工段由高温电解水系统替代，通过提供氢气来调整碳氢比，同时避免水气变换工段排放大量CO2。并且，高温电解水为煤气化提供氧气；调整氢气组分后，通过特定吸附工艺高效灵活去除煤气化后多余杂质气体，以解决传统煤气化制化学品碳原子利用率不高、水气变换调整碳氢比造成CO2大量排放的问题。"
                }
            ]
